                       Snail Race (shareware version)
============================================================================


How To Play:
------------
       Snail Race is a one or two player game where you must race the opposing snail to the finish line. There are 2 types of races: a speed race, and a slowness race. In the speed race you must move your mouse as fast as you can to move your snail to the finish line first. In the slowness race, you must move your mouse as slow as possible without stopping. If you stop or you move the mouse too slowlu or back, then your snail is fouled.


